## 📝 COMANDOS (docs/OPERATIONS_RUNBOOK.md + SEEDS.md)
```bash
podman ps                    # Status containers
podman exec -it exitus-db psql -U exitus -d exitusdb
podman exec -it exitus-backend alembic upgrade head
./scripts/reset_and_seed.sh --clean --seed-type=full  # seed controlado (novo sistema)
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:5000/api/ativos
```

